Please enter the email address where you wish the confirmation code to be<br>
sent.  This will occur immediately, so once done you should be able to<br>
read it momentarily.  Once you have recieved the message and learned your<br>
code, you may use it to create a character.  If you enter an invalid<br>
email address the message will just bounce and you will not be able to<br>
create a new character due to lack of confirmation code.<br>
